      <header>
        <h1>Checkout: Getting Started</h1>
        <p><strong>Storing your Payment Information with Stripe</strong></p>
      </header>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <h1>Account Registration</h1>
          <p>Click "<strong>Remember me</strong>" to securely store your credit card info for faster checkout on this and other sites that use Stripe.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h1>One-Click Payments</h1>
          <p>On this computer, when you come back to

          any other participating site, your credit card info will

          already be filled in: just click <strong>Pay</strong> to confirm your purchase.</p>
          <p>You can edit the card number if you need to. Stripe will store the one you used most recently.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h1>Authentication</h1>
          <p>Your credit card is linked to your <strong>email address</strong> and your <strong>mobile phone number</strong>.</p>
          <p>To pay with Stripe on a different computer, or after you log out, just enter your email address during checkout and Stripe will instantly send you a text message to verify your identity.</p>
          <p>Message and data rates may apply. Frequency of messages depends on user. For help, reply back with HELP. To stop, reply back with <strong>STOP</strong>.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>
